CrossoverTopFrequency: Frequency of the crossover between this band and the next. The last band will have this property ignored
AttackTimeMsec: The amount of time to ramp into any dynamics processing effect in milliseconds.
ReleaseTimeMsec: The amount of time to release the dynamics processing effect in milliseconds
ThresholdDb: The threshold at which to perform a dynamics processing operation
Ratio: The dynamics processor ratio -- has different meaning depending on the processor type.
KneeBandwidthDb: The knee bandwidth of the compressor to use in dB
InputGainDb: The input gain of the dynamics processor in dB
OutputGainDb: The output gain of the dynamics processor in dB
